Golf Memberships
Golf Memberships
Golf membership at Eagle Ridge Golf Club is the most affordable way to get complete access to the best golf courses outside of the The Villages.
Our unlimited golf memberships are designed for snow birds and locals and provide a number of additional incredible benefits.
The layout of our golf facility encompasses 36 holes and have been designed to offer four unique 9-hole golf courses. This design allows us to assemble a number of varying 18 hole golf courses to keep your golf experience from becoming stale.
The Champions, The Masters, The Heritage, and The Memorial courses provide virtually endless opportunities to challenge your game and to enjoy the best golfing experience in Florida.
Eagle Ridge Golf Club is the perfect choice for your home golf course. Since we opened in 1998, golfers from Florida and around the country have graced our courses and left with unforgettable memories.
If you want a golf facility that will pamper your friends and guests, then consider Eagle Ridge Golf Club.
Club Amenities
Unlimited Golf
Use of Practice Facilities with Discounted Range Plan
All Trail Fees Included
Member’s Grandchildren Play FREE after Noon with the Member
Access to the GreatLIFE Golf Network
20% Discount on Soft Goods

About Us
About the Golf Course
Eagle Ridge Golf Club has provided Summerfield and The Villages residents a premier golf experience since 1999. Our four unique courses provide 36 beautiful holes to challenge your golf game while providing all-around fun.
The hardest thing you’ll have to do is decide whether to play one or play all!
Full Practice Facilities
Make your time at Eagle Ridge well spent! A few minutes on our practice range or our putting green will help you tune your swing and stretch those muscles before you hit the course. If you are looking to take things a step further, speak with one of our professional staff about scheduling a lesson or two.
Golf Lessons
Golf Shop
To meet all your golf equipment and apparel needs while at Eagle Ridge Golf Club, we continuously stock our Golf Pro Shop. In our shop you can comfortably browse through all sorts of clubs, equipment, and golf accessories.
You will also find a wide assortment of garments ranging from shirts, golf gloves, hats, shorts, and socks for both men and women.
